#include<bits/stdc++.h>
#include<cstdio>
using namespace std;
main()
{
	long int n,q,t;
	vector< long int >v;
	long int i,j,k;
	long int max_ele,min_ele;
	scanf("%ld",&n);
	scanf("%ld",&q);
	for(i=0;i<n;i++)
	{
		scanf("%ld",&t);
		v.push_back(t);
	}
	max_ele = *max_element(v.begin(),v.end());
	min_ele = *min_element(v.begin(),v.end());
	while(q--)
	{
		scanf("%ld",&t);
		if(t>=min_ele && t<=max_ele)
			printf("Yes\n");
		else
			printf("No\n");
	}
}
